
Simple service monitor software with sms notifications

This is generic framework designed to execute monitoring threads
and send failure and success notitifaction using a GSM modem phone.

Requirements

JavaComm: http://smslib.googlecode.com/files/javacomm20-win32.zip
A GSM phone & drivers

This application uses SmsLib (http://code.google.com/p/smslib/)

I have no plans to extend the application in the near future. 
If you need more functionality fork the source code and have fun!
